Release details, version LTS.395.1
Patch LTS.395.1 of January 23, 2024
Changes and improvements
Stabilizations in file uploading and downloading;
The process of file attachment for Etl was changed;
Making edits was optimized in the eDoc module.
Update package LTS.395.0 of January 16, 2024
New features
A possibility to process "diffDate" and "employeeOnSubordination" functions was added to the filtering algorithm for the list of functions used in autocalculation.
New possibilities of working with visibility algorithms are now available in the Edoc editor.
An option allowing saving the username in external calls is added to GreenData messenger.
Changes and improvements
A mini-help with the description of fields was added to the schedule (CRON-format);
An expression was added to automatically fill in the Receive.Port attribute of the Mail Account;
The registry header was improved with some elements redesigned;
Guf creation became more friendly, in particular when dealing with widget templates, ratings, filters and filtering algorithms;
Improvements in autocalculation and dealing with the condition tree and filtering algorithms;
The possibility of using attrByVar and attr functions was restored for "Algorithm. ETL" algorithm type;
An attribute filter for splitting by intervals was added to Kanban board settings;
Other minor Kanban board improvements like object opening in a new window, viewing the task expected completion date etc.;
System terminology updates;
Corrections in the "Exchange rate data" object type;
Improvements in opening Edoc documents from the registry;
Performance improvements in object profile opening and data loading;
Corrections in the "Basic registry settings" boolean attributes;
Updating improvements when using HTML in bookmark source;
Optimizations in "Checkbox with a hyperlink", "Status bar" and "Reactions and comments to the object" widgets;
An option of multiline display is now available for multiselect attributes as well;
Improvements in getComment function;
A notification added when exiting the login page constructor without saving;
A process of sorting data when working with registries was stabilized;
Optimizations in ETL settings when getting connected to an external DB;
Corrections in setting up the current date and time by user PC settings;
Security improvements when loading PDF files with active contents;
Improvements in connecting to an external call room.
